          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Common Professional Applications :</strong></p><ul><li>Stress & autonomic nervous system assessment</li><li>Functional balance and regulation monitoring</li><li>Before / after session comparison</li><li>Preventive follow-up over time</li><li>Support for therapeutic session evaluation</li><li>Objective visualization for client feedback</li><li>Data collection for structured practice</li><li>Research and evidence-informed approaches</li></ul>",
