        "text": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Position your practice at the forefront of modern wellness with Bio-Well, a scientific tool designed to enrich your therapeutic work and strengthen your professional credibility.</p><p>Using advanced GDV technology, Bio-Well provides real-time visual feedback on stress levels, balance, and vitality. These insights help you better understand your clients’ physiological responses and fine-tune your sessions with greater accuracy.</p><p>By integrating objective measurements—such as energetic balance tracking or session before/after comparisons—you expand your range of services and create new opportunities for value-added consultations.</p><p>Clear, visual data fosters trust and engagement. Clients see, understand, and feel the difference, reinforcing their confidence in your approach and encouraging long-term follow-up.</p><p>Bio-Well supports a practice that is structured, evidence-informed, and aligned with the future of integrative wellness.</p>",
            "text_font": "body",
            "text_size": "subtext-md",
            "text_max_size": 32,
            "text_line_height": 1.6,
            "text_letter_spacing": 0,
            "text_capitalize": false,
